    "http://purl.org/dc/terms/source": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "1. Certification signed by the Municipal Mayor with the following supporting documents:\na. Ereccion de los Pueblos de Cagayan 1863-1898 Tomo VII, provided by the National Archives of the Philippines to the said municipality;\nb. Census of the Philippine Islands: 1903, Volume Two;\nc. RA 7809 dated 16 September 1994;\nd. Sangguniang Bayan Resolution No. 2026-12-058, dated 09 February 2026;\ne. The Biography of General Manuel Sanchez Mira\n\n2. Letter of the NHCP recommending the use of the barangay’s name based on historical records, dated 06 February 2025."
      }
    ],
